<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;h2&gt;Life Insurance — Wealth Tool&lt;/h2&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;p&gt;Life insurance isn't just protection — it's one of the most tax-efficient wealth tools available to families.&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;div class="callout green"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;span class="ci"&gt;✅&lt;/span&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key benefit:&lt;/strong&gt; Death benefits pass income-tax-free. Permanent policies build cash value that grows tax-deferred and can be borrowed tax-free in retirement.&lt;/span&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;div class="ins-grid"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;div class="ins-card ins-term"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;span class="ins-tag"&gt;Term Life&lt;/span&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;h4&gt;Pure Protection&lt;/h4&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;ul&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;10, 20, or 30 year coverage&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Lowest monthly premium&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;No cash value buildup&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Best for: Young families&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;$500K / 20yr ≈ $25–40/mo&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;/ul&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>&lt;div class="ins-card ins-whole"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;span class="ins-tag"&gt;Whole Life&lt;/span&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;h4&gt;Lifetime + Cash Value&lt;/h4&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;ul&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Never expires&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Guaranteed cash value growth&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Fixed premiums for life&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Best for: Estate planning&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Dividends can be reinvested&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;/ul&gt;</p>
