<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;S&amp;P-linked cash value&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;0% floor — no market losses&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Cap on gains (~10–14%)&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">          </span>&lt;li&gt;Best for: Tax-free retirement&lt;/li&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span>&lt;/ul&gt;</p>
